text: One Magnificent Mile (or One Mag Mile) is a mixed-use high-rise tower located in Chicago, Illinois. It was completed in 1983 at the northern end of Michigan Avenue on the Magnificent Mile. It stands at 673.01 ft (205 m). ==Related pages== * List of tallest buildings in Chicago ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Skyscrapers in Chicago Category:1983 establishments in Illinois
title: One Magnificent Mile
